						"copy": "As Cloudflare customers face new challenges with hybrid work, generative AI, and evolving compliance, the CISO Guide to SASE offers a solution. SASE integrates security and networking on a single cloud platform, helping you:\n\n- Drive growth by removing security barriers.\n- Enhance visibility and control across all locations and apps\n- Reduce complexity and costs through vendor consolidation\n- Enable seamless connectivity across networks and users\n\nDownload now to discover how SASE can transform your IT with the CISO Guide to SASE, designed for Cloudflare customers.\n\n![Executive guide: CISOs guide to SASE adoption - Thumbnail](//cf-assets.www.cloudflare.com/slt3lc6tev37/4tYHCbIqUnfrqIk4rWv1KL/870d50c7cc32af084381b7850401e61f/Executive-guide-CISOs-guide-to-SASE-adoption-thumbnail.png)",
